title: LF duo partner (solo/duo queue)
body:
Hello, I am a support main looking for someone easygoing to duo with in ranked. I was plat in S7, unranked in S8 due to a year-long hiatus and placed in iron during the preseason. I would prefer someone around my age (mid-twenties).

Something to note: I'm quite socially anxious and so you can probably expect not to see me talk much during a game.

Add me in game or leave a message here. Thanks.

replies.body: I am quite interested if you dont mind a current Silver3 adc main.
well i would but my age is quite different
I would be interested i just sent a friend request.
